0x1064fb316b88f0464bff4dd7234fcbe18df246.description: True Network aims to create a distributed knowledge graph powered by AI agents to enhance innovation and problem-solving capabilities. By enabling individuals with specialized knowledge to contribute to this network, it seeks to generate tailored insights and insights across domains while preserving user privacy.
0x1064fb316b88f0464bff4dd7234fcbe18df246.aiSummary: True Network aims to create a distributed knowledge graph powered by AI agents to enhance innovation and problem-solving capabilities. By enabling individuals with specialized knowledge to contribute to this network, it seeks to generate tailored insights and insights across domains while preserving user privacy.
0x1064fb316b88f0464bff4dd7234fcbe18df246.businessModel: The company operates on a pay-per-token model where the value derived from queries is distributed among specialized agents and evaluators, with a share allocated to the protocol for development and operational costs.
keyHighlights: Proof of concept demonstrating system speed and functionality
Ability to generate high-quality, specialized insights for users
Engages a vast pool of potential knowledge providers, including millions of PhD holders
Privacy-preserving mechanisms ensuring user data security
Projected growth in the agentic AI market from $5B to over $180B by 2030
riskFactors: Challenges in managing the speed of multiple concurrent agents
Increasing costs associated with the inference of multiple agents
Potential issues surrounding user trust and data privacy

0x8a3f244786ce78f2c7f1ed458d910779998656.description: Founders at Work is a collection of interviews with the founders of successful startups, providing insights into their early days and the challenges they faced. The book aims to showcase the real productivity and innovative spirit of startups, contrasting them with conventional corporate culture.
